Film4.uk.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Tom Cruise stars in part six of the action-thriller series. His mission: to stop terrorists from getting their hands on nuclear bombs and unleashing global devastation.

Film4.uk.title: Scarface
Film4.uk.description: (1983) Al Pacino stars in Brian De Palma's classic crime thriller. A Cuban immigrant uses the coaine trade to take what he wants of the American dream. Say hello to my little friend.

Film4.uk.title: Muppets from Space
Film4.uk.description: (1999) The Muppets are back in another feature-length adventure as Gonzo, convinced that he is of alien origin, struggles to communicate with his family in outer space.

Film4.uk.title: The Seeker: The Dark Is Rising
Film4.uk.description: (2007) Supernatural thriller. Alexander Ludwig stars as The Seeker, who has the task of finding six items hidden throughout time, which the scary forces of The Dark are also looking for.

Film4.uk.title: Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Oscar-winning animated superhero adventure with the voices of Shameik Moore, Kathryn Hahn and Nicolas Cage. Can a gang of Spider-heroes save the universe from reality-bending chaos?

Film4.uk.title: Tooth Fairy
Film4.uk.description: (2010) Family fantasy comedy. Dwayne Johnson stars as a tough ice hockey player who is transformed into a real-life fairy as punishment for telling a child that tooth fairies don't exist.

Film4.uk.title: Dog
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Poignant road-trip comedy with Channing Tatum. A soldier with PTSD must escort a traumatised army canine to a comrade's funeral. Can man and dog save each other's lives?

Film4.uk.title: Commando
Film4.uk.description: (1985) Thriller starring Arnold Schwarzenegger. To free his kidnapped daughter, an ex US commando must agree to assassinate a South American president. But he's not as pliant as he seems...

Film4.uk.title: American Woman
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Emotional drama starring Sienna Miller. A woman must raise her grandson after her daughter disappears. With Christina Hendricks and Aaron Paul.

Film4.uk.title: You Are Not My Mother
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Excruciatingly eerie family horror about a teenage girl who believes her mother has been swapped out after disappearing for a few days. Are there dark forces at work?

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: The Desert Fox
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Drama. James Mason stars in Henry Hathaway's sympathetic portrait of Field Marshal Erwin Rommel in the final years of his life during the Second World War. With Jessica Tandy.

Film4.uk.title: Anastasia
Film4.uk.description: (1956) Historical drama. The Oscar-winning Ingrid Bergman stars as an amnesiac refugee who Yul Brynner tries to pass off as the daughter of the murdered Tsar of Russia, Nicholas II.

Film4.uk.title: Pool of London
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Classic Ealing thriller filmed in a documentary style, starring Bonar Colleano as a sailor whose smuggling activities lead to him being suspected of murder and going on the run.

Film4.uk.title: Rio Grande
Film4.uk.description: (1950) Western. John Wayne plays the commander of a Texan fort at which his ex-wife (Maureen O'Hara) pitches up. Can he win back her love by saving kidnapped children from Apache raiders?

Film4.uk.title: Flight of the Phoenix
Film4.uk.description: (2004) Drama. Dennis Quaid stars as the captain of an aircraft downed in the desert. There's no hope of rescue, unless he and the survivors can build another plane from the wreckage.

Film4.uk.title: Top Gun: Maverick
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Danger-zone action as Tom Cruise returns to the cockpit after 36 years. He's Maverick. He still feels the need for speed. And there's a near-impossible mission to fly. With Jon Hamm.

Film4.uk.title: Io Capitano
Film4.uk.description: (2023) Matteo Garrone's heartfelt, harrowing drama about two Senegalese lads who make a dangerous journey across the Sahara to make their fortune as singers in Europe. English subs.

Film4.uk.title: The Guard
Film4.uk.description: (2011) Comedy crime thriller starring Brendan Gleeson and Don Cheadle. A dead body and an FBI agent disrupt a rule-bending policeman's laid-back life on the west coast of Ireland.

Film4.uk.title: A Lawless Street
Film4.uk.description: (1955) A non-stop romp of a western from director Joseph H Lewis. In the town of Medicine Bend, only Marshal Calem Ware can keep its citizens from falling into complete lawlessness.

Film4.uk.title: The Frogmen
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Second World War thriller. Richard Widmark, Dana Andrews and Robert Wagner star as divers with a special underwater demolition team taking the war to the Japanese in the Pacific.

Film4.uk.title: Henry VIII and His Six Wives
Film4.uk.description: (1972) Historical drama with Keith Michell as Henry VIII, nobly supported by Donald Pleasance, Charlotte Rampling and Jane Asher. The dying monarch reviews his own life.

Film4.uk.title: The Violent Men
Film4.uk.description: (1955) Cold War-influenced western starring Glenn Ford and Edward G Robinson. A smallholder stands alone against the expansionist plans and brutal tactics of a tyrannical rancher.

Film4.uk.title: Fatherhood
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Heartfelt fact-based comedy-drama. Kevin Hart stars as a widower who is suddenly sprung into single fatherhood after his wife dies a day after giving birth.
(2023) Sci-fi action adventure starring Adam Driver as a spaceman who crash-lands on a strange planet where giant lizards stalk the darkness... 65 million years ago. Where on Earth is he?

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Subaru Impreza: Dave's in fast car heaven as he picks up a rare Subaru Impreza and an equally powerful Ford Escort RS Cosworth from North Wales. S7 Ep12

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Morgan Plus 8/Clenet Roadster: Derek rubs shoulders with pop music royalty when he picks up a Morgan sports car; a WWII ambulance arrives at Thornton le Dale and a Ford Model T needs a new home. S5 Ep

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Audi Quattro/Sunbeam Alpine: The Mathewsons welcome a 1982 Audi Quattro and a Sunbeam Alpine, and Derek takes delivery of a beautiful green Renault van previously used to carry bread in Paris. S5 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Austin Gipsy/Toyota MR2 Ferrari: Derek heads to Scotland in the mother of all rainstorms to pick up a Jaguar E-type and a rare MGC convertible. Plus, Dave extracts a rare Austin Gipsey from a lock up.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Ford Thames 400E/Vauxhall Astra: Derek collects a Ford Thames 400E that once belonged to the pop band Edison Lighthouse. Plus, Dave heads to York to collect an Astra GTE convertible. S5 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Ford Zodiac Estate/Toledo: Derek picks up a rare Ford Zodiac Farnham Estate, while Dave heads for an isolated tent in the Midlands to collect a Triumph Toledo. S5 Ep5

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Teleshopping
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Shopping from Home.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Great Continental Railway Journeys
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Palermo to Mt Etna: On a railway journey from the capital Palermo to Europe's largest volcano, Mount Etna, Michael Portillo explores Sicilian life under Mussolini. S7 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Great Continental Railway Journeys
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Linz to Bratislava: Michael Portillo travels by train through Austria and the Czech Republic, beginning in the northern Austrian city of Linz, where Adolf Hitler lived as a boy. S7 Ep5

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Great Indian Railway Journeys
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Amritsar to Shimla: Guided by his Bradshaw's 1913 Handbook of Indian, Foreign and Colonial Travel, Michael Portillo embarks on a rail journey from Amritsar to Shimla. S1 Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Trawlermen
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: New. The Great Prawn Hunt: Prawn trawlers Amity and Fruitful Bough head for Devil's Hole, where they face a winter storm. While Fruitful Bough fills its nets, Amity battles to stop from sinking. S1 Ep

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Trawlermen
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: New. The Storm: Skipper Jimmy considers whether his prawn trawler Amity should ride out a storm or head for port, and the pressure builds on the Ocean Venture crew. S1 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Trawlermen
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: New. The Edge: Ocean Venture skipper John Buchan takes a risk in the treacherous North Atlantic to find the perfect catch, the Amity crew face a serious setback, and Fruitful Bough heads home. S1 Ep3

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: E Type S2/Escort RS Turbo: A classic car fan with a love of the Jaguar E-Type reluctantly sends his dream car to auction, hoping to buy a motorhome. Two Ford Escorts get Dave's pulse racing. S1 Ep9

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Rolls Silver Shadow/Austin 7: A widow reluctantly parts with her husband's treasured collection of Rolls Royces and Bentleys, and an impulse buyer finds one of the cars a new home. S1 Ep10

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Aston DB2/Merc SL: Jack's off to East Yorkshire for an iconic 80's motor, where a Ford enthusiast is thinning out his herd of nine Escorts. S12 Ep10

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Flipping Bangers
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Alfa Romeo: Gus and Will hunt down an affordable Italian car, and eventually find an Alfa Romeo 155 hiding in a barn. Making space for an inspection proves a challenge. S1 Ep5

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Frozen Planet
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: To the Ends of the Earth: David Attenborough reveals the vast wilderness of the polar regions. At the North Pole, polar bears court and the sun returns after six months of dark. S1 Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Frozen Planet
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Spring: Landmark nature series. See warmth and life return to these magical ice worlds as spring arrives in the polar regions and the sun appears after an absence of five months. S1 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Frozen Planet
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Summer: David Attenborough's visually stunning nature series. The sun never sets over summer in the polar regions. See how hordes of animals exploit this brief window of plenty. S1 Ep3

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Frozen Planet
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Autumn: Witness how solar landscapes change as the big freeze returns. Most animals leave on epic journeys, some battle to breed and for a few it is a time of opportunity. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Ireland with Simon Reeve
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Simon begins his journey in the south of Ireland by paramotoring with an Irish explorer before doing a spot of surfing and climbing Croagh Patrick in honour of Ireland's patron saint. S1 Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Flipping Bangers

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Sunbeam Lotus/Morris Minor Convert: Dave finds a very rare 70s Sunbeam Lotus that has been rotting away in a farmyard for 29 years, while a Morris Minor convertible goes under the hammer. S2 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: E Type/Austin A35: A delightful collection of British classics comes up for auction, including an Austin A35 and a Hillman Avenger Estate in stunning condition. An E-Type Jaguar also hits the auction.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: MGB GT/Morris Minor Police Car: Three MGs from the 70s turn up at the garage, still covered in original factory wax. Nobody can believe it, or value them. A Morris 1000 turns up at the auction. S2 Ep6

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash: Restoring Classics
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Project X / Beach Cruiser: The team buy one of Derek's favourite Austin commercials and convert it to electric, and also snap up a super-rare 50's American beach bike. S6 Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Shopping from Home.
